Third-party notices — CopyPaste for Android
=============================================

This file lists third-party assets vendored (not linked as a Maven
dependency) into this module's source tree, and their licenses.

Lucide icons
------------

Path geometry for the glyphs under
`app/src/main/java/com/copypaste/android/ui/theme/icons/` is vendored from
lucide-icons/lucide (https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide) at tag
v0.265.0, commit 9fb4b0b161fc256d2333f91812a927f2ed6f84c0, converted from SVG
`<path>`/`<circle>`/`<line>`/`<rect>`/`<polyline>` data to Kotlin
`androidx.compose.ui.graphics.vector.ImageVector` source by
`scripts/generate-lucide-icons.sh` (+ `generate-lucide-icons.mjs`). No
Lucide-Compose Maven artifact is used — see design.md's "Resolved decisions"
(android-material3-redesign) for why: every published Lucide-Compose
artifact requires kotlin-stdlib >= 2.0, incompatible with this workspace's
Kotlin 1.9.23.

