Tooling deviation note (DevSrSouza/svg-to-compose)
---------------------------------------------------

design.md's S0.3 spike named `DevSrSouza/svg-to-compose` (MIT) as the
primary conversion tool. As of 2026-07-02 that project has no artifact
resolvable from Maven Central or JitPack (JitPack returns 404 with no build
triggered), so it was not actually invoked anywhere in this pipeline — no
svg-to-compose source or binary is vendored or executed, and no MIT notice
is owed for it. `generate-lucide-icons.mjs` is an independently written
SVG-path -> Compose PathBuilder DSL converter (design.md's pre-authorized
"hand-port" fallback for this exact case). See bd issue CopyPaste-myh8.2
notes for the full rationale.
